item.title: Getting started
item.description: Installation From Source If you have Go installed and GOPATH environment variable properly set up, you can download and install cloudprober using the following commands: go get github.com/google/cloudprober GOBIN=$GOPATH/bin go install $GOPATH/src/github.com/google/cloudprober/cmd/cloudprober.go Pre-built Binaries You can download the pre-built binaries for Linux, Mac OS and Windows from the project’s releases page.
